keyMappings:
# Unmap default keys
unmap h
unmap J
unmap K
unmap t
unmap gt
unmap gT
unmap g0
unmap g$
unmap j
unmap x
unmap X
unmap H
unmap L

map k scrollDown
map l scrollUp

# Tab Navigation
map tn createTab
map tk previousTab
map tl nextTab
map tj firstTab
map t; lastTab
map tq removeTab
map tu restoreTab
map J goBack
map : goForward
